<view class="login-page data-v-ab1f8938"><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['chooseAvatar',['$event']]]]]}}" class="login-logo data-v-ab1f8938" bindtap="__e"><block wx:if="{{avatarUrl}}"><image class="avatar-img data-v-ab1f8938" src="{{avatarUrl}}"></image></block><block wx:else><text class="data-v-ab1f8938">🐻</text></block></view><view class="login-title data-v-ab1f8938">小棕熊预约报名</view><view class="login-desc data-v-ab1f8938">活动预约 · 培训报名 · 场馆预约</view><view class="login-card data-v-ab1f8938"><view class="wx-info data-v-ab1f8938"><button class="avatar-btn data-v-ab1f8938" open-type="chooseAvatar" data-event-opts="{{[['chooseavatar',[['onChooseAvatar',['$event']]]]]}}" bindchooseavatar="__e"><block wx:if="{{avatarUrl}}"><image class="wx-avatar data-v-ab1f8938" src="{{avatarUrl}}" mode="aspectFill"></image></block><block wx:else><text class="avatar-placeholder data-v-ab1f8938">📷</text></block></button><view class="wx-name-box data-v-ab1f8938"><input class="nickname-input data-v-ab1f8938" type="nickname" placeholder="点击获取微信昵称" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','nickname','$event',[]]]]]]}}" value="{{nickname}}" bindinput="__e"/><text class="wx-tip data-v-ab1f8938">自动获取微信身份信息</text></view></view><view class="agree-row data-v-ab1f8938"><checkbox style="transform:scale(0.7);" checked="{{agreed}}" color="#D4720D" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['e0',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e" class="data-v-ab1f8938"></checkbox><text class="agree-text data-v-ab1f8938">我已阅读并同意</text><text data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['goPrivacy',['$event']]]]]}}" class="agree-link data-v-ab1f8938" catchtap="__e">《用户服务协议及隐私政策》</text></view><button class="wx-phone-btn data-v-ab1f8938" open-type="getPhoneNumber" disabled="{{!agreed}}" data-event-opts="{{[['getphonenumber',[['handleWechatPhone',['$event']]]]]}}" bindgetphonenumber="__e"><text class="wx-icon data-v-ab1f8938">💬</text><text class="data-v-ab1f8938">微信手机号快捷登录</text></button><text class="bottom-tip data-v-ab1f8938">点击上方按钮，授权手机号即可登录</tex